material.
</emphasis>
<typeStatus box="[339,443,685,710]" pageId="4" pageNumber="279">Holotype</typeStatus>
♀ [examined], with dissected epigyne (epigyne was lost during manipulations). Vial labels: “Hangtoheou A. Pichon” and “Potanin 
<number box="[706,737,721,746]" pageId="4" pageNumber="279" value="85.0">85</number>
”. Text data “Hangtseheou, Tschekiang, 
<number box="[1213,1274,721,746]" pageId="4" pageNumber="279" value="1925.0">1925</number>
